	<p id = 'p1_text'>Welcome to RosettaClone, a website designed to mimic the basic functionality and usefulness of Rosetta Stone, a language learning tool. The idea
	behind this program is to use visual and audio cues to facilitate the learning of a new language.</p>
	<div></div>
	<p id="p2_text">There are 4 pages to choose from on this site. The first is this homepage. The second is a guessing game where a word is shown, and the user must match the correct picture
	to the word. The third is a fill-in-the-blank style game, where a user must add the correct adjective to a sentence. Finally, there is a feedback page where a user can write and send
	feedback to the OSU server.</p>



